title: Hokies end 2-game skid with 28-13 victory over Wolfpack
text: Hokies end 2-game skid with 28-13 victory over Wolfpack Saturday, 10 October 2015 (3 minutes ago) BLACKSBURG, Va. (AP) Brenden Motley and Isaiah Ford teamed up for three second-quarter touchdown passes Friday night and Virginia Tech found a winning formula at home again in a 28-13 victory against North Carolina State.
